data.comment: The whistle has gone to start the match.
Fred Onyedinma (Wycombe) has received a first yellow card.
In the minute 13, Goal! Andre Ayew gives Swansea a 0-1 lead in Wycombe.
Jake Bidwell with an assist there.
Great finish from Jamal Lowe to give Swansea a 0-2 lead.
In the minute 23, Great play from Andre Ayew to set up the goal.
Geoff Eltringham blows to end the first-half.
The second-half is underway in Wycombe.
In the minute 69, The home team replace Fred Onyedinma with Daryl Horgan.
Gareth Ainsworth (Wycombe) is making a second substitution, with Josh Parker replacing Matt Bloomfield.
The away team have replaced Jamal Lowe with Liam Cullen. This is the first substitution made today by Steve Cooper.
In the minute 82, Jay Fulton is on a sub for Morgan Gibbs-White for Swansea.
Gareth Ainsworth is making the team's third substitution at Adams Park with Scott Kashket replacing David Wheeler.
Josh Parker for Wycombe has been booked by Geoff Eltringham and receives a first yellow card.
That's full-time at Adams Park. The final score is 0-2.
